            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%83%E6%B2%A1%E7%86%9F%E9%80%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E8%95%89%E4%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E9%87%8D%E4%BE%BF%E7%A7%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%83%E6%B2%A1%E7%86%9F%E9%80%8F%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E8%95%89%E4%BC%9A%E5%8A%A0%E9%87%8D%E4%BE%BF%E7%A7%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#吃没熟透的香蕉会加重便秘#</span></a>！缓解便秘还得是熟香蕉<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%95%BF%E9%BB%91%E6%96%91%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E8%95%89%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E4%BE%BF%E7%A7%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%95%BF%E9%BB%91%E6%96%91%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E8%95%89%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E4%BE%BF%E7%A7%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#长黑斑的香蕉才能缓解便秘#</span></a> 不少人觉得吃香蕉可以缓解便秘，医生提醒，想通过吃香蕉补充膳食纤维含量来缓解便秘，需要吃8根~10根，甚至更多。并且，不太成熟的香蕉中含有一定的鞣酸和抗性淀粉，二者结合后吸干粪便中的水分，反而可能会造成便秘。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6CFtNqD" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
